{"tid":2000961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個IG特別on9嘅小粉紅","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T08:54:06.000Z","uid":355943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db884becb53961c9d4364766f1c6d3570cae22a5","tid":2000961,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:54:07.000Z","msg":"我係IG其中一個文宣人<br />\n入面通常有啲好on9嘅小糞紅<br />\n依家最出名有兩個 ak仔 同埋kimi<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">ak仔</span><br />\nak仔成日講 我打遊戲輸，話我哋係大陸仔鄉下仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日用廿三條威脅人 咩立咗法之後你哋就死得 瘋狂用emoji洗版 話搵到你ip之後殺咗你 點知個ip都係一樣(老作)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">ak仔 IG</span>(其中一個ac，唔知佢有幾多個ac)<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/ak4770527?igshid=1508amvdze6kc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fak4770527%3Figshid%3D1508amvdze6kc&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=54c30d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/ak4770527?igshid=1508amvdze6kc</a> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/05/04/150606_ddc35d6ea7633390643dd9ff23adc77e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F05%2F04%2F150606_ddc35d6ea7633390643dd9ff23adc77e.jpg&h=6f10b130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">kimi</span><br />\n之前好似普通文宣acc屌下共慘党<br />\n近期佢偷另外一個文宣ac幅相做Profile相<br />\n之後仲誣告返受害人偷佢profile相<br />\n呢件事之後 用分化，藍絲狗等之眼攻擊受害人 其他人幫拖 用一模一樣嘅招數反擊 呢件事到而家冇停過 <br />\n近期開始反美 分化手足 屌任何屬於黃嘅嘢 狂開ac做一模一樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (已知有八個)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">kimi IG</span>(主ac)<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/kimi221125?igshid=v1v3qkra0w7x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fkimi221125%3Figshid%3Dv1v3qkra0w7x&d=LQBsT8b49a